dup of 2.3X and an average compression ratio\nimprovement of 2.0X over cuZFP under the same data distortion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Apr 2023 03:55:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 2 May 2023 19:04:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-04"}
