rried by them. By harnessing the long-range\nspin-Hall transport of exciton polaritons, we have demonstrated two novel room\ntemperature polaritonic devices, namely the NOT gate and the spin-polarized\nbeam splitter, advancing the frontier of room-temperature polaritonics in\nperovskite microcavities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Apr 2023 14:26:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-26"}
