arder, but metastable structures (e.g.,\nmetastable VN, TaN, ReN$_2$, Cr$_3$N$_4$, and ZrB$_6$ possess high hardness).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Apr 2023 14:51:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-26"}
