ic and product datasets verify that PIMM outperforms state-of-the-art\nbaselines. Moreover, we deploy the PIMM in a large-scale FinTech platform, and\nthe online experiments also demonstrate the effectiveness of PIMM.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Apr 2023 07:55:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-03"}
